Mike, come on out.

00:05:56.030 --> 00:05:59.719
Do helmets reduce the
incidents of atherosclerosis

00:05:59.719 --> 00:06:03.408
to aid in their own survival
because the host lives longer

00:06:03.408 --> 00:06:04.408
so they can?

00:06:05.866 --> 00:06:08.201
- Thanks for the question.

00:06:08.201 --> 00:06:12.052
There's nothing that worms
can't do, apparently.

00:06:12.052 --> 00:06:12.952
No, it's a good question.

00:06:12.952 --> 00:06:16.232
I think there's a variety of ways, yeah

00:06:16.232 --> 00:06:20.554
helmets aren't trying to make
changes in our human bodies

00:06:20.554 --> 00:06:22.943
just for our own benefit but, you know,

00:06:22.943 --> 00:06:26.983
they're trying to ensure
their own growth and survival.

00:06:26.983 --> 00:06:29.431
Now, intestinal helmets don't
reproduce inside the body

00:06:29.431 --> 00:06:33.113
but of course, you know they
lead to the shedding of eggs

00:06:33.113 --> 00:06:37.280
which will permit to spread
and so there's a variety

00:06:38.196 --> 00:06:42.381
of different ways that helmets
actually exert their effects.

00:06:42.381 --> 00:06:46.422
They're taking lipids,
consuming lipids and glucose

00:06:46.422 --> 00:06:49.614
from our bodies, they're
altering the way that lipids

00:06:49.614 --> 00:06:53.861
