them, and so the dynamic

00:07:35.070 --> 00:07:38.839
we're actually still
trying to work this out

00:07:38.839 --> 00:07:43.561
how helmets have co-evolved
with our immune system

00:07:43.561 --> 00:07:46.721
in ways that our body almost
expects them to exist.

00:07:46.721 --> 00:07:47.554
